Most people miss this completely,  Connectors run as tasks inside a Connect worker.

3
00:00:13,881 --> 00:00:21,947
Workers can be standalone (single process) or distributed (cluster, recommended for production).

4
00:00:21,947 --> 00:00:29,802
Plot twist: Most production implementations of this,  are , actually FREE and open source.

